  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771120/extras/04e257e167faefd263ce38c3aa0b9272.avif?t=1703562410\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><strong>Solo Path</strong><br> Is an escape game with horror and Urbex themes.<br>You will play as Ethan, a fan of urban exploration who goes to visit a mysterious abandoned complex.<br>Unfortunately not everything is going to go as planned and this could well be his last exploration.<br><br><br>Prepare your brain, a paper and a pen, and have your heart set on!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771120/extras/fa5cae0e9e2e74ab49ff67bb2ce31434.poster.avif?t=1703562410\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771120/extras/fa5cae0e9e2e74ab49ff67bb2ce31434.webm?t=1703562410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771120/extras/fa5cae0e9e2e74ab49ff67bb2ce31434.mp4?t=1703562410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br>Solo Path is a scripted game in first person view.<br>The gameplay is based on exploration, collecting clues, solving puzzles and quests.<br>All in a heavy atmosphere with a scary, evolving and mysterious scenario.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771120/extras/84c024c47d7c341e925beed5e8ab255c.poster.avif?t=1703562410\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771120/extras/84c024c47d7c341e925beed5e8ab255c.webm?t=1703562410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771120/extras/84c024c47d7c341e925beed5e8ab255c.mp4?t=1703562410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Solo Dev <br>Solo Game <br>Solo Path",
